{"tid":1431814,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"珀玥開放式呎租73元 貴絕新界","createTime":"2019-08-08T05:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:23:59.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fd5b11937e4e1e5d5d2675b4b1cc0f25030d8ed4","tid":1431814,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:34:06.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】雖然社會持續動盪，但入伙新盤租金再創新高，其中大圍珀玥為近年首批主打納米單位的新界新盤之一，已於近月陸續入伙，新近錄得首宗租務成交，實用面積201方呎的1房戶呎租高達73元，創新界呎租新高。<br />\n<br />\n美聯首席高級營業經理陳國浩表示，珀玥高層C室，實用面積201方呎，屬1房間隔，新近獲租客以月租1.46萬元承租，實用呎租約72.6元，呎租不但創沙田區新高，亦貴過市區納米樓。業主2018年7月以509.83萬元一手購入，現租金回報約3.4厘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.28hse.com/2019/07/874924_2019074477.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.28hse.com%2F2019%2F07%2F874924_2019074477.jpg&h=7766b4bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71cd6328ac1cb80f71750a9d07d94a00239990ae","tid":1431814,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af48a720fb70cade0be2f69a1e4ad20bd14876dd","tid":1431814,"uid":75355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"201方呎 1房間隔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc9b89bf2681131ffdda3c662062f6d4bf3467c","tid":1431814,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/BmepMAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmepMAH.jpg&h=0ea49d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Yz5gCHn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYz5gCHn.png&h=a502547a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/